<template>
  <el-date-picker
    :placeholder="$t('i18nView.datePlaceholder')"
    @change="doChange"
    clearable
    type="date"
    v-model="dateValue"
    value-format="yyyy-MM-dd">
  </el-date-picker>
</template>

<script>

  export default {
    name: 'DatePicker',
    props: {
      disabled: {
        type: Boolean,
        required: false
      },
      value: {
        type: String
      }
    },
    mounted() {
      this.dateValue = this.value
      if (this.disabled) {
        this.isDisabled = this.disabled
      }
    },
    methods: {
      doChange(val) {
        this.$emit('change', val)
      }

    },
    data() {
      return {
        dateValue: '',
        isDisabled: false
      }
    },
    watch: {
      value(val, oldVal) {
        this.dateValue = val
      },
      dateValue(val, oldVal) {
        if (val != oldVal) {
          this.$emit('input', this.dateValue)
        }
      },
      disabled(val, oldVal) {
        if (val != oldVal) {
          this.isDisabled = val
        }
      }

    },
    computed: {}
  }
</script>


<style>

</style>
